Article: May 10 Citizens Financial Group Inc* Announces pricing of $1.0 billion of Citizens Bank NA senior notes  * Pricing of note offering by Citizens Bank NA of $1 billion principal amount of 2.550% notes due May 13, 2021, at an issue price of 99.907%  Source text for Eikon:  Further company coverage:    (Bengaluru Newsroom: +1-646-223-8780)
Title: BRIEF-Citizens Financial Group announces pricing of $1 bln of Citizens Bank NA senior notes
